MBALI KHANYILE SIYANDA isibalo sabasebenzi bezempilo abahaqwa yiCovid-19 KwaZulu-Natal. UNgqongqoshe wezempilo kulesi sifundazwe uNkk Nomagugu Simelane-Zulu,  uthe umnyango uthole emasontweni edlule ukuthi siyanda isibalo asabasebenzi bezempilo abatheleleka ngegciwane. Uthe kubona kubalwa osonhlalakahle, odokotela, omabhalane, abahlengikazi nabanye abasebenza ngaphakathi ezibhedlela ezehlukene esifundazweni. Ngokwezibalo zomnyanyo bangu-38 abasebenzi okutholakale ukuthi baneCovid-19 e-Addington kule nyanga. Kulesi sibalo kubalwa odokotela abahlanu, abahlengikazi abangu-11, nabasebenzi abangu-22 abalekelela emagunjini eziguli.